task.summary: storing zoom and color mode in a shared preference. hiding buttons which don't have any support for the current device.
Do not adjust the brightness automatically, because some users may have problems with the high value.
Optimized performance slightly by increasing thread number.
Added an alternative way to receive a bitmap from the YUVImage. Works, its greyscaled, but slow as the compressToJpeg. But the quality is much better!

Increased performance for some devices. Using the original "camera preview" if no_filter is applied, which has a drastically performance boost. Using a yuv to greyscale-rgb instead of jpeg-compression to have a lossless image as result and apply filters to the greyscaled bitmap. Added a pause Button to the view to pause the camera preview. Additionally added the feature to switch color modes in paused mode.
ToastMsg for "Saved Image". Icons added. Process Bitmap as RGB if we've freezed the camera preview.
Don't need to re-create the bitmap if we toggle color modes in paused mode.
Hiding flash button if we're in paused mode. Fixed taking a screenshot.
fixed bug: start / stop camera preview.
